  "text": "Whole cell lysate preparation and regular WB were performed as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Preparation of NF and CF was conducted using a protein extraction kit (Beyotime P0027) according to the manufacturer's instruction. For enhanced WB analysis, the SuperSignal Western Blot Enhancer kit (Thermo 46640) was employed to enhance detection sensitivity.",
